Please find attached our acknowledgement of your representation of Jasmine
Wilson, her declarations page, Personal Injury Protection application, and
medical authorization.
Please note on the deciarations page that there is a $1,000 PIP deductible
that must be met prior to making any payments. This amount will be equally
distributed among Jasmine and Julian Wilson.
Please provide the following information for our file:
What are your client's injuries from this accident?
Where has your client treated since the accident and where will she seek
further treatment? If she treated at the ER, did she go by ambulance?
Where was your client coming from and going to? Was your client on the job
at the time of the accident?
Did your client lose any wages? If so, please advise her employer's name and
address, occupation, payrate, and how long she was/may be off work. (We'll
need off work notes from a treating physician and wage documentation from an
employer).
Any prior injuries and, if so, who treated her?
We need to confirm her residential address and if she is insured by Medicare
or Medicaid. If so, we need his Medicare Beneficiary ID number (MBI #) and
Social Security Number.
I look forward to working with you.
